You are working on agent.gate, a standalone governance and observability engine.

Product positioning:
- Always refer to the product as "agent.gate" in user-facing copy.
- This is NOT SonarQube.
- This has no dependency on the Domino REST API.

Technical guidance:
- Prefer policy-driven governance workflows and explicit auditability.
- Keep telemetry naming under the `agent.gate.*` namespace.
- Keep issue/violation metric naming under `agent.gate.issues.*`.
